secubox-turn (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release - TURN/STUN server management for WebRTC
  * FastAPI backend with coturn integration
  * Service control (start/stop/restart)
  * User management with turnadmin
  * Temporary credential generation using HMAC-SHA1
  * Active session monitoring
  * Configuration editor for turnserver.conf
  * Realm settings management
  * P31 Phosphor light theme frontend
  * Three-fold architecture (Components/Status/Access)

